00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:50.440
light" and we are just going to play around
with the "constant" and as you can see it

00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:56.620
really makes it darker and it brings in the
colour a bit more, so I'm going to go for

00:02:56.620 --> 00:03:05.300
